{"tid":918131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 美國或向 iPhone 及手提電腦徵收 10% 關稅","createTime":"2018-11-27T03:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T09:35:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2b646f11db3b93b2e9f248e4d54627a2c98de3","tid":918131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T03:29:53.000Z","msg":"Nov 27, 2018<br />\n由於中美貿戰的關係，主力在中國組裝生產的 iPhone、MacBook 可能會成為下一輪被徵收關稅的目標。華爾街日報於周一訪問美國統 Donald Trump，Trump 表示正考慮向 iPhone、手提電腦徵收關稅。他表示徵收關稅是有可能的，只是看收多少，他指可以收取 10% 關稅，而人們也會較易接受。<br />\n<br />\n如果 iPhone 真的要被徵收 10% 關稅，Apple 的產品在美國的售價有可能調高，暫時未知 Apple 會如何回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/11/27/iphone-face-10-pcs-tariffs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F11%2F27%2Fiphone-face-10-pcs-tariffs%2F&d=kPlvPdLcVkc%2Fw3cbopP%2FZi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=88dc0956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/11/27/iphone-face-10-pcs-tariffs/</a>"},{"pid":"15c059a42ec65e503d6c0ee0aee2879105820a43","tid":918131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\napple die soon"},{"pid":"1de55bfd7c33b717d88d8e0433b96db5bc0902cf","tid":918131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T03:30:51.000Z","msg":"已經少人買，仲要加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6922ec0a2bd5cece1d4c42fe8f117c2c4e3c7d65","tid":918131,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T03:32:18.000Z","msg":"好呀，made in usa <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d74b7f0b275d4205a29